                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="message">
                This verification proves that your document is the exact same file that was originally uploaded to DocChain. You can be confident in its authenticity and integrity.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div>Thank you for using DocChain - Where Trust is Replaced by Cryptography</div>
            <div class="timestamp">Email sent on {{currentDate}} at {{currentTime}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
